# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:19
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_40fbd539:

    # "I drive out to the go-kart track and meet Reba there."
    "Dirijo até à pista de karting e encontro-me com a Reba lá."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:24
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_5a90113c:

    # rb "Oh dang, are we even going to fit in these tiny things?"
    rb "Caramba, será que vamos caber nestas coisinhas minúsculas?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:25
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_724d59ff:

    # rb "I haven't been to one of these places since I was a little kid."
    rb "Não vou a um sítio destes desde que era criança."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:26
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_394fd056:

    # rb "I think the last time I came, it was my cousin's birthday or something."
    rb "Acho que da última vez que vim foi no aniversário do meu primo ou algo do género."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:27
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_c3947180:

    # "While we wait for our turn to drive, we have some time to chat."
    "Enquanto esperamos pela nossa vez de conduzir, temos algum tempo para conversar."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:33
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_dba2e530:

    # "Finally, it's our turn."
    "Finalmente, é a nossa vez."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:36
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_8f9b8839:

    # "We line up and get ready to take off."
    "Alinhamos e preparamo-nos para arrancar."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:38
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_e4323b18:

    # rb "Hope you're ready to get your butt smoked."
    rb "Espero que estejas pronta para levares uma coça."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:39
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_53dbc1f5:

    # pc "Yeah right. You're going down."
    pc "Pois, claro. Vais perder."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:40
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_359c7155:

    # rb "Maybe later!"
    rb "Talvez mais tarde!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:47
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_26aa19ac:

    # "When the light comes on and the buzzer sounds, she pulls in front very quickly. My kart is not accelerating as fast as hers, no matter how much I mash on the gas."
    "Quando a luz acende e o alarme soa, ela arranca muito rapidamente. O meu kart não acelera tão depressa como o dela, por mais que eu carregue no acelerador."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:54
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_1ec15e0c:

    # "As much as I try to catch up, she's just too fast. She takes the corners perfectly, barely letting off the accelerator."
    "Por mais que tente alcançá-la, ela é simplesmente demasiado rápida. Ela faz as curvas na perfeição, mal tirando o pé do acelerador."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:60
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_d3f8613e:

    # "By the end of our time, she is well in the lead, leaving me far behind."
    "No final do nosso tempo, ela está bem na liderança, deixando-me muito para trás."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:67
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_855b783c:

    # "But once I'm able to get the kart up to top speed, I start catching up with her."
    "Mas assim que consigo levar o kart à velocidade máxima, começo a alcançá-la."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:73
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_349acc4b:

    # "Then, on the final lap, I'm barely able to slip past her just before we cross the finish line."
    "Então, na última volta, consigo ultrapassá-la por pouco mesmo antes de cruzarmos a linha de chegada."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:78
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_8661faca:

    # rb "Woo! I smoked your butt!"
    rb "Uau! Derrotei-te!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:79
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_65fb2eea:

    # pc "What does that even mean?"
    pc "O que é que isso significa?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:80
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_21896d0c:

    # rb "Means you got smoked!"
    rb "Significa que foste derrotado!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:83
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_1781f259:

    # rb "Dang, that sucked. My car was slow."
    rb "Bolas, que chatice. O meu carro era lento."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:84
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_049951bc:

    # rb "I bet if I had like ten minutes with that engine, I could give it more power. Then you wouldn't stand a chance."
    rb "Aposto que se tivesse uns dez minutos com aquele motor, conseguia dar-lhe mais potência. Aí não terias hipótese nenhuma."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaDates/rebagokartdate.rpy:85
translate portuguese rebagokartdatestart_5d928b84:

    # pc "I believe it."
    pc "Acredito nisso."

